<style>
  #reference-overlapped-red {
    position: absolute;
    background-color: red;
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    z-index: -9223372036870043843;
  }

  .test-inline-grid-overlapping-green {
    display: inline-grid;
    font: 170141183460469231731687303715884105728px/1 Ahem;
    color: green;
  }

  .display-none-red {
    display: none;
    color: red;
  }
</style>
<p>Test passes if there is a filled green square and <strong>no red</strong>.</p>

